snippet: Shanshan Feng birdied five of her first nine holes to shoot a seven-under 65 and take a four-stroke lead after the second round of the Dubai Ladies Masters.
abstract: Shanshan Feng takes second-round at Dubai Ladies Masters golf tournament.
